## DECISION ARTIFACT

The decision is a markdown document (grammar: `.agent/artifact-formats/planning_analysis_decision.md`):
`---` frontmatter with `type: planning_analysis_decision` and `status: completed|request_changes|failed`,
then `## Summary` (exactly one item), and — for any non-completed status — `## What Came Up Short`
and `## How To Fix`, one `- [PA-###] ...` item per gap with matching IDs across the two sections.

- Choose `status: completed` when the plan is sound across ALL evaluatable dimensions.
- Choose `status: request_changes` when it falls short in any evaluatable dimension with a gap you proved yourself.
- Choose `status: failed` when the analysis found major incompleteness or an otherwise unusable plan; stronger remediation may be needed, including starting over from the planning phase.

Author the document, submit it per the procedure below, and only then call {{DECLARE_COMPLETE_TOOL_REFERENCE}}.

{% set planning_decision_example %}
---
type: planning_analysis_decision
status: request_changes
---

## Summary
- [SUM-1] The plan is missing executor-ready verification.

## What Came Up Short
- [PA-001] Dimension: Verification gap | Defect: verification section omits the exact pytest command | Evidence: V-1 says "run tests" | Missing: exact command and expected passing result

## How To Fix
- [PA-001] Rewrite the Verification section with method `pytest tests/test_foo.py -q` and an `Expect:` field describing the passing regression test, then resubmit the plan document.
{% endset %}
